import React, { useState } from 'react';
import { 
  Container, 
  Typography, 
  Box, 
  Paper, 
  List, 
  ListItem, 
  ListItemIcon, 
  ListItemText, 
  Button, 
  Divider, 
  useTheme, 
  useMediaQuery,
  CircularProgress,
  Alert  // Add this import
} from '@mui/material';
import { styled } from '@mui/system';
import PersonIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Person';
import ClassIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Class';
import TournamentIcon from '@mui/icons-material/EmojiEvents';
import CodeIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Code';
import SmartToyIcon from '@mui/icons-material/SmartToy';
import VideogameAssetIcon from '@mui/icons-material/VideogameAsset';
import LeaderboardIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Leaderboard';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';

const WelcomeContainer = styled(Container)(({ theme }) => ({
  paddingTop: theme.spacing(5),
  paddingBottom: theme.spacing(5),
}));

const WelcomeBanner = styled(Box)(({ theme }) => ({
  background: `linear-gradient(135deg, ${theme.palette.primary.main} 0%, ${theme.palette.primary.dark} 100%)`,
  padding: theme.spacing(4),
  borderRadius: theme.shape.borderRadius,
  color: theme.palette.primary.contrastText,
  marginBottom: theme.spacing(4),
  boxShadow: theme.shadows[3],
  position: 'relative',
  overflow: 'hidden',
  '&::after': {
    content: '""',
    position: 'absolute',
    top: 0,
    left: 0,
    right: 0,
    bottom: 0,
    backgroundImage: 'url(/chess-pattern.png)',
    backgroundSize: '100px',
    opacity: 0.1,
    zIndex: 1,
  },
}));

const UserWelcome = styled(Paper)(({ theme }) => ({
  padding: theme.spacing(3),
  marginBottom: theme.spacing(4),
  borderRadius: theme.shape.borderRadius,
  backgroundColor: theme.palette.background.paper,
  boxShadow: theme.shadows[2],
  transition: 'transform 0.3s ease-in-out',
  '&:hover': {
    transform: 'translateY(-5px)',
    boxShadow: theme.shadows[4],
  },
}));

const DashboardContainer = styled(Paper)(({ theme, userRole }) => ({
  padding: theme.spacing(3),
  borderRadius: theme.shape.borderRadius,
  backgroundColor: userRole === 'teacher' 
    ? 'rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.08)'
    : 'rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.08)',
  marginTop: theme.spacing(4),
  boxShadow: theme.shadows[1],
}));

const DashboardButton = styled(Button)(({ theme }) => ({
  marginTop: theme.spacing(2),
  fontWeight: 'bold',
}));

const StyledListItem = styled(ListItem)(({ theme }) => ({
  paddingLeft: 0,
}));

const HomePage = ({ toggleTheme, mode, userData }) => {
  const theme = useTheme();
  const isMobile = useMediaQuery(theme.breakpoints.down('sm'));
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);
  const [error, setError] = useState(null);

  if (loading) {
    return (
      <Box display="flex" justifyContent="center" alignItems="center" minHeight="80vh">
        <CircularProgress />
      </Box>
    );
  }

  if (!userData) {
    return (
      <Box display="flex" justifyContent="center" alignItems="center" minHeight="80vh">
        <Typography>No user data available</Typography>
      </Box>
    );
  }

  return (
    <WelcomeContainer maxWidth="md">
      {error && (
        <Alert severity="warning" sx={{ mb: 3 }}>
          {error}
        </Alert>
      )}
      
      <WelcomeBanner>
        <Typography variant={isMobile ? "h4" : "h3"} component="h1" gutterBottom fontWeight="bold">
          Welcome to Chess Bot Tournament Platform
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="subtitle1">
          Create, test, and compete with your chess bots against others
        </Typography>
      </WelcomeBanner>

      <UserWelcome elevation={2}>
        <Typography variant="h5" component="h2" gutterBottom color="primary">
          Hello, {userData.email}
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body1">
          You are logged in as a <Box component="span" fontWeight="bold">{userData.role}</Box>
        </Typography>
      </UserWelcome>

      <Box mb={4}>
        <Typography variant="h5" component="h3" gutterBottom>
          Platform Overview
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
          This platform allows students to create, test, and compete with chess bots against other students.
          Design your own chess algorithm and see how it performs against others!
        </Typography>
        <Divider />
      </Box>

      {userData.role === 'teacher' ? (
        <DashboardContainer elevation={1} userRole="teacher">
          <Typography variant="h5" component="h3" gutterBottom>
            Teacher Dashboard
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
            As a teacher, you can:
          </Typography>
          <List>
            <StyledListItem>
              <ListItemIcon>
                <ClassIcon color="primary" />
              </ListItemIcon>
              <ListItemText primary="Create and manage classes" />
            </StyledListItem>

            <StyledListItem>
              <ListItemIcon>
                <PersonIcon color="primary" />
              </ListItemIcon>
              <ListItemText primary="View student progress" />
            </StyledListItem>

            <StyledListItem>
              <ListItemIcon>
                <TournamentIcon color="primary" />
              </ListItemIcon>
              <ListItemText primary="Organize tournaments" />
            </StyledListItem>

            <StyledListItem>
              <ListItemIcon>
                <CodeIcon color="primary" />
              </ListItemIcon>
              <ListItemText primary="Review student code" />
            </StyledListItem>
          </List>
          <DashboardButton 
            variant="contained" 
            color="primary" 
            component={Link} 
            to="/dashboard"
            fullWidth={isMobile}
          >
            Go to Dashboard
          </DashboardButton>
        </DashboardContainer>
      ) : (
        <DashboardContainer elevation={1} userRole="student">
          <Typography variant="h5" component="h3" gutterBottom>
            Student Dashboard
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
            As a student, you can:
          </Typography>
          <List>
            <StyledListItem>
              <ListItemIcon>
                <SmartToyIcon color="primary" />
              </ListItemIcon>
              <ListItemText primary="Create and train your chess bot" />
            </StyledListItem>

            <StyledListItem>
              <ListItemIcon>
                <VideogameAssetIcon color="primary" />
              </ListItemIcon>
              <ListItemText primary="Test your bot against built-in opponents" />
            </StyledListItem>

            <StyledListItem>
              <ListItemIcon>
                <TournamentIcon color="primary" />
              </ListItemIcon>
              <ListItemText primary="Compete in tournaments" />
            </StyledListItem>

            <StyledListItem>
              <ListItemIcon>
                <LeaderboardIcon color="primary" />
              </ListItemIcon>
              <ListItemText primary="View your progress and rankings" />
            </StyledListItem>
          </List>
          <DashboardButton 
            variant="contained" 
            color="primary" 
            component={Link} 
            to="/dashboard"
            fullWidth={isMobile}
          >
            Go to Dashboard
          </DashboardButton>
        </DashboardContainer>
      )}
    </WelcomeContainer>
  );
};

export default HomePage;
